Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GİTHOMO KĨA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Job 19: 1, 23-27a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi ĩo Job agīcokia akīūria atīrī: 
Na arī korūo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciugo ciakwa  nīkwandikwo ikīandikĩtwo! </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-60}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Korũo nĩ gútemwo itemetwo thĩinĩ wa ibuku! 
Na arī korūo icanītwo </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na karamu ga kigera na igekīrūo ngocorai, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo itûūre ii njane ndūmba-inī ya ihiga kinya tene!</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
No ningî nî njūĩ atĩrĩ: atī Müngũũri arī o kuo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>e muoyo, na at</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> marigīririo-inī nīwe ükarūgama tiri-inī ůyū; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ikonde ici ciakwa ciakīrikia kwiha, na mwirí wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ůyũ wa nyama wagīkorūo ndũri ho, hĩndi îo nĩ ngona Ngai;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ kwionera ngamwionera arī wa mwena wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maitho makwa nĩmo makamwirorera, na tĩ ta e mūgeni.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERÜO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi 27: 1:4; 7,8b.9a; 13-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata
ühonokio wakwa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Mwathani nīwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata ūhonokio
wakwa; ingīgītigīra ū? </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩwe hinya ūrīa
ügitiire muoyo wakwa; ūrīa ūngīmakia nū?</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA:</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata
ühonokio wakwa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Ndĩ ūndū ũmwe nyendete harī Mwathani, 
na nīguo ndithingataga; </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nî atī njikarage nyūmba ya Mwathani
matukū mothe ma muoyo wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndīīonagīre wega wa Mwathani, 
na adīîtuiragirie ūhoro kũu thĩinī wa
hekarŭ yake.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA:</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata
ühonokio wakwa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Mwathani, igua mügambo wakwa ngikaya;
kĩnginyīrie wega waku, ūnyamükīrie. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Üthiù waku, Mwathani, nĩ ndĩrīũrongoragia. Tiga kwīīhithĩra ūthiŭ waku.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA:</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata
ühonokio wakwa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Guca njĩikitie at</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nĩ ngeyonera wega wa Mwathani
ndĩ bũr</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ri wa arīa me muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ingīri kũhooteka Eterera o Mwathani: </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gīa na hinya, na wĩũmĩrīrie
ngoro; î-nī, no gīeterere Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA:</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩwe ūtheri wakwa, o gwata
ühonokio wakwa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GİTHOMO KÍA IGİRİ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aroma 5: 5-11</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA MARŨA
MA M</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>Ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>THURE PAULO KŪRÍ AROMA</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariû a lthe witū, wĩrigirĩro ndũngīgatūma mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akehokokwo, nî gũkor</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>o wendani wa Ngai ni ũitiriirūo </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngoro-inī ciitū nĩ ũndũ wa gūikarūo nĩ Muoyo Mūtheru
ürīa twaheirūo,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu-rī, hĩndi îrīa twatŭire twagīte hinya-rī, 
o ihinda rīrīa rīagirire riakinya, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristü nī aakuire ithe
nya rīa andũ othe matatīaga Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rîrī, nĩ hinya mūndŭ etikīre kũragwo ithenya rīa mūndū ũngi,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ūrīa mūthingu, no hihi kwahota kuoneka mūndũ</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūngiūmiriria kūragwo o ūguo, ithenya rĩa mũndũ mwega. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩri, ündũ Uria Ngai onanītie ūtwendi wake
naguo-rĩ, nĩ ûyũ, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tī Kristũ aatūkuirtire ri rīa twatūire tũrī o ehia. </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riu, kuona atī nĩ tůrīkītie gūtuwo
athingu nĩ ũndū wa thakame yake-rī,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makīria o na kūhonoka tūkahonoka kwi marakara ma Ngai nĩ</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ůndũ wake, Amu-ri, akorūoo rĩria twatůire tūrī thũ ciake,</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twaiguithanirio na Ngai na njira îo ya gūkua kwa Mĩirī,
rĩu tūkirī aiguithanie nake, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o makīria tũkahonoka nî</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ndũ wa
ūguni wa muoyo wake. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na to üguonwiki, no ningī nĩ twĩrahaga nĩ gükenera Ngai, nĩ ũndū </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ũrĩa tùgunītwo nî Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristů, 
arī we ütūmite rīu tügie na ũiguithanio.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RÜÏMBO RWA ALLELUYA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>John 6, 40</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu ărīa Awa ekwenda nī atīri, atĩ
mũndū o wothe ūrorete Mūriũ, na akamwihoka, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīe na muoyo wa tene na tene; na niĩ nĩ ngamūriūkia
mūthenya wa kūrigīrĩria. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GİTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>John 6: 37-40</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŰTHOMA INJIRI YA M</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>Ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>THURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi îo agīgīta Kirindi na akīmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aria othe Ithe witů aheete no magoka kūrĩ ni</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>; </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mūndũ ükīte kūr</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> niĩ ndingĩmūingatao na atīa. </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu-rī, ndiumīte Igūrŭ ngoka gwīka ūrīa ngwenda nii mwene,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no urīa ekwenda ũrĩa wandekirie. Na ũrĩa ekwenda, úcio wandekirie, nī atrĩri, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ atĩ aria othe aheete ndigate o na ūmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no ndĩmariūkie mūthenya wa kùrigiriria. Amu ūrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa ekwenda nĩ atīrī, atī mũndū o wothe ůrorete Mūriũ, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na akamwihoka, agīe na muoyo wa tene na tene;</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na níĩ nĩ ngamūriūkia mūthenya wa kūrigīrīria.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.59.51_59c5109c.jpg"}},
Text:"KÍRIRIKANO KĨA AKUŬ MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"aVAJJATnm0+C6JntWJ6Jlw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_14696bf5.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>KUWAKUMBUKA WAAMINI MAREHEMU WOTE</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO KUTOKA AGANO LA KALE
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Ayubu 19:1, 23-27a</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Ayubu</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ayubu alijibu:
Ningetaka maneno yangu yaandikwa</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningetaka yachorwe katika gombo,
yachongwe milele katika mwamba</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa patasi ya chuma na kwa risasi!
Mimi najua kwamba Mwokozi wangu yu hai,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwamba atasimama juu ya mavumbi, yeye wa mwisho </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami, nikivikwa ngozi yangu, nitasimama wima</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na katika mwili wangu nitamwona Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami nitamwona mimi mwenyewe, wala si mwingine.”</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 23:1-3,4, 3,8</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu,
sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hunipumzisha katika malisho mabichi;
hunipeleka kwenye maji matulivu;</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hunipatia nguvu.
Huniongoza katika njia zilizo sawa
kwa ajili ya jina lake. K</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata nijapopita katika bonde la giza,
siogopi mabaya, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwani wewe upo pamoja nami;
gongo lako na fimbo yako vyanituliza. K.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waandaa meza mbele yangu,
machoni pa adui zangu;</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umenipaka mafuta kichwani;
kikombe changu kinafurika. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kweli, wema na fadhili zitanifuata
siku zote za maisha yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitakaa nyumbani mwa Bwana
kwa miaka mingi ijayo. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO KUTOKA AGANO JIPYA
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Ufunuo 21:1-5a, 6b-7</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo kutoka kitabu cha Ufunuo wa Mtakatifu Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbingu ya kwanza na ulimwengu wa kwanza vilikuwa vimepita,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi, Yohane, niliona mbingu mpya na nchi mpya kwani</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na bahari haipo tena. Nikauona mii mtakatifu, Yerusalemu mpya,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukishuka kutoka mbinguni kwa Mungu. Umetayarishwa kama bibi</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>harusi aliyejipamba kwa aj ili ya mume wake.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nikasikia sauti kubwa kutoka kiti cha enzi ikisema, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Tazama hema ya Mungu kati ya wanadamu. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye atakaa kwao, nao watakuwa taifa lake </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Mungu mwenyewe atakuwa pamoja nao.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atafuta kila chozi katika macho yao. 
Hakutakuwa tena mauti,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> wala sikitiko, wala kilio, wala maumivu </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwa mambo ya kwanza yatakuwa yamepita.”,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Yeye aliyeketi katika kiti cha enzi akasema: 
“Tazama, nafanya yote upya.” </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ni Alfa na Omega, mwanzo na mwisho.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwenye kiu nitampa cha kunywa </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pasipo malipo katika chemchemi ya maji ya uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ashindaye atarithi haya: 
mimi nitakuwa baba yake naye atakuwa mwanangu.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Mathayo ll:25</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nakutukuza, Baba, Bwana wa mbingu na dunia,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwa umewafunulia watoto wadogo
mafumbo ya ufalme.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Mathayo 5:1-12a</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Alipoyaona makundi ya watu, [Yesu] alipanda juu ya</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mlima, akaketi na wafuasi wake wakamjia.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye akafumbua kinywa chake, akawafundisha akisema:</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Heri walio maskini wa roho,
maana ufalme wa mbinguni ni wao.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri walio na huzuni, maana hao watatulizwa.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri walio wapole, maana hao watairithi nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri walio na njaa na kiu ya uadilifu, maana hao watashibishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri walio na huruma, maana hao watapata huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri walio na moyo safi, maana hao watamwona Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri wapatanishi, maana wataitwa wana wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri wanaodhulumiwa kwa ajili ya haki,
maana ufalme wa mbingu ni wao.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Heri ninyi watu wakiwatukana na kuwadhulumu</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwasingizia vibaya kwa uongo kwa ajili yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Furahini, shangilieni,
kwa kuwa thawabu yenu ni kubwa mbinguni.”</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.59.51_59c5109c.jpg"}},
